    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Refers to the third of the four divisions of La Tène art as defined by Paul Jacobsthal in 1944. It is characterized by the incorporation of faceted, chunky, bossed, and curved elements. Jacobsthal's La Tène style sequence has been challenged by modern scholars.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000000/VP</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000099620/Legacy AAT data</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Se refiere a la tercera de cuatro divisiones del arte La Tène definido por Paul Jacobsthal en 1944. Se caracteriza por la incorporación de elementos con lados rechonchos, tachonados y encorvados. La secuencia de estilos Jacobsthal La Tène ha sido cuestionada por estudiosos modernos.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Spanish</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000131/CDBP-SNPC</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000051034/TAA database (2000-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Verwijst naar de derde van de vier divisies van La Tène art die Paul Jacopbsthal in 1944 heeft geformuleerd. Het kenmerkt zich door het gebruik van gefacetteerde, oneffen, gebosseleerde en gebogen elementen. De La Tène-stijlindeling van Jacobsthal wordt door moderne onderzoekers ter discussie gesteld.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Dutch</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
          <Note_Contributor>
            <Contributor_id>10000205/AAT-Ned</Contributor_id>
          </Note_Contributor>
        </Note_Contributors>
        <Note_Sources>
          <Note_Source>
            <Source>
              <Source_ID>2000113770/AAT-Ned (1994-)</Source_ID>
            </Source>
          </Note_Source>
        </Note_Sources>
      </Descriptive_Note>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>指稱由保羅‧傑柯布斯索（Paul Jacobsthal）於一九四四年針對拉田藝術所做出的四個時期中的的第三時期。此風格的特徵為將融合兼併平面、厚片、浮刻與曲線元素。當代學者已針對傑柯布斯索的風格分期順序提出諸多質疑。</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>Chinese (traditional)</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
